SUMMARY:Banff Mountain Film Festival @ Rocknasium
DESCRIPTION:Rocknasium in Davis is excited to host another year of the Banff Mountain Film Festival world tour! The evening will feature different multiple award-winning films that explore adventure\, environmental issues\, and action sports. There will also be a prize draw during intermission with prizes from Banff international sponsors & local Davis sponsors!
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/banff-mountain-film-festival-rocknasium/
LOCATION:Richard Brunelle Performance Hall\, 315 W 14th Street\, DAVIS\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="Rocknasium the Climbing Gym":MAILTO:info@rocknasium.com
